# Run Tests Before PR

- Before commit/PR for test changes, run the new or changed test(s) with the correct project (usually `smoke-app` or `smoke-ai`).
- Prefer a targeted filter (`-g "test name"`) over the full suite for speed; run the owning smoke file when in doubt.
- Do not open a PR for failing tests. Fix and re-run first.
- Mention what was run in the PR test plan (command or test title + pass/fail).
